OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FA hockey coach who claimed his
OL,8,Finterior designer wife stabbed herself
OL,9,Fto death in Worcestershire has been
OL,10,Fjailed for at least 21 years for her
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FMohamed Samak, 43, told a jury his
OL,14,Fwife Joanne Samak, 49, had stabbed
OL,15,Fherself in the chest and stomach after
OL,16,Fhe woke up at around 3am on July 1
OL,17,Flast year at their home in Chestnut
OL,18,FSpinney in Droitwich Spa.
OL,20,FHe was found guilty of murder on
OL,21,FWednesday after a retrial.
