OL,7,FThe former Egyptian international
OL,8,Fhockey player and coach, who worked
OL,9,Fwith the Wales under-18s team, killed
OL,10,Fhis wife because he was suffering
OL,11,Ffinancial problems and had become
OL,12,Finterested in another woman,
OL,13,Fprosecutors said.
OL,15,FSamak told the trial, his wife took
OL,16,Fher own life and was struggling with
OL,17,Falcohol and mental health problems,
OL,18,Falthough friends and family said they
OL,19,Fhad no concerns about her drinking or
OL,20,Fher mental state, and that she had
OL,21,Fthings to look forward to.
