OL,7,FJailing him for life on Friday
OL,8,F(October 31st), Judge James Burbidge
OL,9,FKC said Samak's actions were "wicked
OL,10,Fbeyond comprehension" and he had
OL,11,Fdestroyed the lives of Joanne's family.
OL,13,FHe said: "The emotion you disclose is
OL,14,Feither feigned or emotion based on
OL,15,Fself-pity. I cannot accept you are
OL,16,Fremorseful because you still deny
OL,17,Fresponsibility and put Jo's loved ones
OL,18,Fthrough the trauma of two trials.
