OL,7,F"You sought to besmirch her name by
OL,8,Fsaying she drunk to excess and was not
OL,9,Fin control of her mental faculties.
OL,10,FNothing could have been further from
OL,11,Fthe truth.
OL,13,F"The trial heard she always was a
OL,14,Fwoman who held everything together."
OL,16,FJoanne, who was the main breadwinner
OL,17,Fwhile Samak struggled to find a
OL,18,Fpermanent job, suffered six stab
